('1 On 1 Off', 'Aerobic Base', '["Circuit Board"]', '10', null, '60s', '19 min', 'Moderate Effort', 'Structured mid-intensity intervals with a 1:1 work-to-rest ratio. Climb for 1 minute, rest for 1 minute, and repeat for multiple sets. Intent: Stress your aerobic capacity system with intervals that become progressively harder to recover from by the end of the workout. Descanso: 60s set rest', false),
