('4x4s', 'Power Endurance', '["Training Board"]', '4', '4 reps', null, '32 min', 'Hard Effort', 'Climb 4 boulders back-to-back with little to no rest between problems, then rest before repeating for multiple sets. Intent: Develop aerobic power through high-end efforts with limited rest, using varied boulder movement to push sustained output. Descanso: 5m set rest', false),
('6 in 6', 'Power Endurance', '["Training Board"]', '3', '60s x 6 reps', null, '28 min', 'Very Hard Effort', 'Complete 6 boulders on the minute across multiple sets. The compressed timeframe drives rapid fatigue. Intent: Develop repeated anaerobic output with each boulder completed on the minute. Descanso: 5m set rest', false),
('60% Repeater Test', 'Power Endurance', '["Hangboard"]', '1', '7s x 90 reps', null, '15 min', 'Very Hard Effort', 'Hang at 60% of your two-arm max with a 7-second on, 3-second off cycle and continue until failure. Record your total time to exhaustion. Intent: Test and benchmark your forearm endurance capacity at a standardised submaximal intensity.', true),
('AnCap Project', 'Power Endurance', '["Training Board"]', '6', null, null, '30 min', 'Very Hard Effort', 'Repeat a project-specific or replica boulder across multiple sets, climbing with performance focus. Intent: Transfer anaerobic capacity gains to real-world or project-specific demands. Descanso: 5m set rest', false),
('Boulder Doubles', 'Power Endurance', '["Training Board"]', '6', '2 reps', null, '27 min', 'Very Hard Effort', 'Climb a hard boulder, brief rest, then repeat it immediately. Complete multiple sets of doubles. Intent: Develop anaerobic capacity and the ability to maintain intensity across repeated high-power efforts. Descanso: 4m set rest', false),
('Boulder Mileage Forced Intervals', 'Power Endurance', '["Training Board"]', '2', '20 reps', null, '69 min', 'Hard Effort', 'Complete a high number of mid-range boulders across multiple sets with short rests, ensuring a wide variety of movement. Intent: Push aerobic power by completing a high volume of mid- to high-intensity boulders under fatigue. Descanso: 10m set rest', false),
('Boulder Triples', 'Power Endurance', '["Training Board"]', '5', '3 reps', null, '41 min', 'Very Hard Effort', 'Climb a hard boulder 3 times per set with short rest between reps, completing multiple sets. Intent: Develop anaerobic capacity through repeated high intensity efforts that builds fatigue across reps and the course of the session. Descanso: 5m set rest', false),
('Broken 30s', 'Power Endurance', '["Circuit Board"]', '4', '3 reps', null, '27 min', 'Very Hard Effort', 'Break a 30-move route or circuit into 3 sections of 10 moves, resting 20 seconds between sections. Rest 6 minutes between full laps. Intent: Train performance on sustained climbing by breaking a limit-level route into completable sections. Descanso: 6m set rest', false),
('Extended Boulders', 'Power Endurance', '["Training Board"]', '3', '4 reps', null, '45 min', 'Hard Effort', 'Repeat a long 16-move boulder across multiple sets. Expect to be fighting by the end. Intent: Push tolerance for sustained high-intensity sequences that bridge bouldering and route-length effort. Descanso: 5m set rest', false),
('Harder 5 Sets', 'Power Endurance', '["Circuit Board"]', '5', null, null, '50 min', 'Very Hard Effort', 'Climb 5 hard routes or circuits of 30-40 moves from easiest to hardest. Intent: Improve aerobic power through challenging route-length efforts that prepare you for the demands of hard sport climbing. Descanso: 10m set rest', false),
('Linked Boulders', 'Power Endurance', '["Training Board"]', '3', '4 reps', null, '45 min', 'Hard Effort', 'Repeat a well-rehearsed long boulder problem (around 14 moves) across multiple sets. Intent: Improve tolerance to sustained high-intensity sequences that demand prolonged effort. Descanso: 5m set rest', false),
('Onsighting', 'Power Endurance', '["Lead Wall"]', '4', null, null, '66 min', 'Hard Effort', 'Attempt 4 routes at or near your onsight level on lead, spending time route reading and preparing before each single attempt. Intent: Train aerobic power alongside the tactical and psychological skills needed to perform on onsight attempts. Descanso: 20m set rest', false),
('Route Doubles', 'Power Endurance', '["Circuit Board"]', '5', '2 reps', null, '65 min', 'Hard Effort', 'Climb a hard route, rest briefly on the wall or lower off, then immediately repeat it. Complete 5 double laps with full rest between sets. Intent: Build sustained aerobic power by replicating longer efforts, ensuring a high volume of fatiguing climbing. Descanso: 10m set rest', false),
('Route Projecting', 'Power Endurance', '["Circuit Board"]', null, null, '100m', '100 min', 'Very Hard Effort', 'Spend the workout attempting routes at the limit of your ability, whether projects or hard new climbs. Aim for 150-250 moves total. Intent: Develop top-end power endurance by trying hard routes, building the ability to perform at this level.', false),
('Route Pyramid', 'Power Endurance', '["Circuit Board"]', '8', null, null, '102 min', 'Hard Effort', 'Climb 8 routes in a pyramid, starting easy, building to your hardest, then working back down. If you have fewer sets, stop at the top. Intent: Train aerobic power while completing high-volume route climbing across ascending and descending intensities. Descanso: 10m set rest', false),
('Board Efficiency', 'Strength and Power', '["Training Board"]', null, null, '60m', '60 min', 'Hard Effort', 'Refine beta and eliminate unnecessary movement on board problems you already know. Focus on climbing as cleanly and efficiently as possible. Intent: Increase technical efficiency and energy economy on steep terrain without needing to get stronger.', false),
('Board Max Efforts', 'Strength and Power', '["Training Board"]', null, null, '60m', '60 min', 'Very Hard Effort', 'Work at true top-end intensity on a training board, attempting problems that will take multiple workouts to complete. Intent: Increase maximal strength and power output on steep board terrain.', false),
('Board Max Efforts - Extended', 'Strength and Power', '["Training Board"]', null, null, '120m', '120 min', 'Very Hard Effort', 'An extended board workout at true top-end intensity, with more time to work limit problems and accumulate quality attempts. Intent: Increase maximal strength and power output with a higher volume of top-end effort.', false),
('Board Pauses', 'Strength and Power', '["Training Board"]', '4', '3 reps', null, '45 min', 'Hard Effort', 'On each move of a steep board problem, cut your feet loose and hold for 3 seconds before replacing them. Maintain control throughout. Intent: Develop contact strength, shoulder stability, and positional control under load. Descanso: 5m set rest', false),
('Board Sending', 'Strength and Power', '["Training Board"]', null, null, '60m', '60 min', 'Hard Effort', 'Attempt board problems just under your limit that you can complete within a few attempts. Aim for high-quality sends rather than long-term projects. Intent: Build confidence and performance capacity on steep board terrain through successful execution of hard problems.', false),
('Board Session', 'Strength and Power', '["Training Board"]', '6', null, '6m', '66 min', 'Very Hard Effort', 'Climb hard problems on a training board with 3 attempts per problem and full recovery between sets. Intent: Build top-end strength and power while improving your ability to execute hard moves on steep board terrain. Descanso: 6m set rest', false),
('Board Volume', 'Strength and Power', '["Training Board"]', null, null, '60m', '60 min', 'Hard Effort', 'Accumulate a high number of challenging board problems at submaximal intensity, completing each within 1-3 attempts before moving on. Intent: Build work capacity and strength endurance on steep terrain through consistent, high-volume effort.', false),
('Boulder Circuits', 'Strength and Power', '["Circuit Board"]', '6', '3 reps', null, '55 min', 'Hard Effort', 'Follow a circuit or pick boulders within a given grade range, working problems just above flash level with structured sets. Intent: Build submaximal strength and movement variety through consistent, repeatable effort across a range of problems. Descanso: 6m set rest', false),
('Boulder Focus', 'Strength and Power', '["Boulder Wall"]', '10', null, '20s', '30 min', 'Very Hard Effort', 'Target a specific technical theme or movement style throughout the workout, as directed by your coach. Execute with precision. Intent: Address individual technical weaknesses while maintaining a strength stimulus. Descanso: 3m set rest', false),
('Boulder Max Efforts', 'Strength and Power', '["Training Board"]', null, null, '60m', '60 min', 'Very Hard Effort', 'Attempt boulder problems at the limit of your ability with full recovery between attempts. Problems may take multiple workouts to complete. Intent: Increase maximal strength and power output.', false),
('Boulder Mileage', 'Strength and Power', '["Training Board"]', '20', null, '3m', '60 min', 'Hard Effort', 'Complete 20 boulders in one hour at a challenging but manageable intensity, aiming to flash or complete each within two attempts. Intent: Build capacity and tolerance for sustained, high-volume bouldering at a controlled mid-intensity.', false),
('Boulder Play', 'Strength and Power', '["Training Board"]', null, null, '60m', '60 min', 'Hard but playful', 'Experiment with movement in a low-pressure stimulus by creating or modifying problems. Try unfamiliar styles, beta, and body positions. Intent: Expand movement vocabulary, coordination, and creative problem-solving.', false),
('Boulder Pyramid', 'Strength and Power', '["Training Board"]', '15', null, null, '50 min', 'Moderate to Max', 'Climb progressively harder problems up to your max, then work back down through easier grades. If you have fewer sets, stop at the top. Intent: Develop strength and fatigue management through controlled intensity variation across a structured pyramid. Descanso: 2m 30s set rest', false),
('Boulder Sending', 'Strength and Power', '["Training Board"]', null, null, '60m', '60 min', 'Hard Effort', 'Attempt problems that are difficult but achievable within a few tries. Prioritise successful sends and precise execution. Intent: Reinforce performance consistency while building submaximal strength and power.', false),
('Campus - 3 Moves', 'Strength and Power', '["Campus Board"]', '8', null, null, '22 min', 'Very Hard Effort', 'Perform 3 maximal campus moves per set across multiple sets, focusing on speed and controlled contact on each rung. Intent: Increase peak pulling power and contact strength through extended maximal campus sequences. Descanso: 3m set rest', false),
