('Flashing Boulders', 'Strength and Power', '["Boulder Wall"]', '14', null, '4m', '95 min', 'Hard Effort', 'Commit fully to single-attempt flash efforts on problems at your flash grade across a variety of styles. Route read carefully, then give 100%. Intent: Improve flash ability, decision-making, and high-pressure execution. Descanso: 3m set rest', false),
