('Side Split Iso - Static Active', 'Flexibility', '["Bodyweight"]', '3', null, '60s', '5 min', 'Deep Stretch', 'Hold a side split position while actively engaging your muscles to maintain the stretch for timed holds. Intent: Build active strength and control at side split depth, developing usable range of motion for wide climbing positions. Descanso: 60s set rest', false),
('Side Split Test - Unsupported', 'Flexibility', '["Bodyweight"]', null, null, '30s', '1 min', 'Deep Stretch', 'Perform an unsupported side split ISO hold to record your current side split performance, with notes and measures tracked over time. Intent: Benchmark your side split progress through a standardised test, allowing you and your coach to track flexibility gains over time.', true),
